{"tid":2282550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"︱浸大再多一體育系學生染疫 為確診女生密切接觸者 本月6日曾回校","createTime":"2020-11-12T02:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T12:28:32.000Z","uid":5195,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9b3e535214e07fe37f79df8fb7bd6e20e5fa5dbd","tid":2282550,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"本港昨日（11日）新增18宗武漢肺炎病例，是上月8日以來最多，其中3宗本地感染皆源頭不明，包括一名23歲浸大女生。至今早浸大向師生發電郵，指再多一名體育系學生確診，該確診者為第5398號個案的緊密接觸者。校方指，該名學生前日（10日）發病，最後一日返校園是本月6日，校方並會追蹤其接觸史。<br />\n<br />\n又有本地 通關無望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7a71ae349df7d291c917cbd9e155ec1845188d","tid":2282550,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:43:21.000Z","msg":"有幾密切<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec182fbf50bcfec875874ba415ebafdfd52b6d0f","tid":2282550,"uid":38533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:43:57.000Z","msg":"停課未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d7a20d7b1c7c3c1a06c98655a1857d1eb3572e","tid":2282550,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:44:34.000Z","msg":"Hall G<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c3a35b4573379fb7a31e21b6a9e44f319a7654","tid":2282550,"uid":26770,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:45:28.000Z","msg":"條女一定好濫<br />\n<br />\n一定貪體育系學生操開下下頂到最深"},{"pid":"809fd094cfc06605bd2a77141e15c5a73b71ce34","tid":2282550,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"96d7a20d7b1c7c3c1a06c98655a1857d1eb3572e","tid":2282550,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:44:34.000Z","msg":"Hall G<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"